Celia Ireland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Celia_Ireland 0 Celia Ireland (born 16 May 1966) is an Australian actress. She is best known for her role as Regina Butcher on the television series All Saints and her Logie award winning role as Liz Birdsworth on the prison drama series Wentworth.
